; Coverage test for filters.cc
; Exercise changed_value_posts revaluation with market value changes.
; The --gain report triggers revaluation logic.

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/02/01 AAPL $160.00

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Broker    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash     $-1500.00

test reg Assets:Broker --gain
24-Feb-01 Commodities revalued  <Revalued>                  $100.00      $100.00
end test
